00:38:38.250 --> 00:38:41.651
970 mile to go!

474
00:38:41.653 --> 00:38:44.187
[laughs]

475
00:38:44.189 --> 00:38:46.089
- To collis p. Huntington.

476
00:38:46.091 --> 00:38:47.991
Director of
central pacific railroad.

477
00:38:47.993 --> 00:38:49.626
Stop.

478
00:38:49.628 --> 00:38:51.094
Sherman peak is behind me.

479
00:38:51.096 --> 00:38:52.462
Stop.

480
00:38:52.464 --> 00:38:54.030
[telegram machine clicking]

481
00:38:54.032 --> 00:38:55.699
I am coming for you.

482
00:38:55.701 --> 00:38:59.202
Stop.
[laughs]

483
00:38:59.204 --> 00:39:02.305
The zebra shall be eaten.

484
00:39:02.307 --> 00:39:03.873
Stop.

485
00:39:03.875 --> 00:39:07.610
[background conversations.
