486
00:39:16.120 --> 00:39:18.788
- Excuse me. I...

487
00:39:28.132 --> 00:39:30.800
Excuse me?

488
00:39:40.911 --> 00:39:44.914
[speaking mandarin]

489
00:39:49.720 --> 00:39:51.187
Name?

490
00:39:51.189 --> 00:39:53.923
- Cullen bohannon.

491
00:39:53.925 --> 00:39:55.158
- Railroad experience?

492
00:39:55.160 --> 00:39:57.160
- More than enough. chan!

493
00:39:57.162 --> 00:39:59.095
More than enough.

494
00:39:59.097 --> 00:40:01.798
[speaking mandarin]

495
00:40:06.537 --> 00:40:11.541
Welcome to the great state
of california. mr. Bohannon.

496
00:40:11.543 --> 00:40:15.311
Ambition get the best of ya?

497
00:40:23.254 --> 00:40:25.855
- I'm here
'til I find my family.

498
00:40:25.857 --> 00:40:29.559
Whatever you can do to help me.
you'll do.

499
00:40:29.561 --> 00:40:30.693
Whatever's my share. I keep.

500
00:40:30.695 --> 00:40:34.664
Whether I'm here a week
or a year.

501
00:40:36.133 --> 00:40:38.268
- Agreed.

502
00:40:38.270 --> 00:40:41.137
- 5% then?

503
00:40:41.139 --> 00:40:44.574
- 1 1/2.

504
00:40:44.576 --> 00:40:46.543
It's a big company.

505
00:40:50.881 --> 00:40:53.383
[laughs]

506
00:40:53.385 --> 00:40:55.919
Come with me!
I want to show you a telegram.

507
00:40:55.921 --> 00:41:00.790
Durant is on the downslope
of sherman peak.

508
00:41:00.792 --> 00:41:03.593
Now...With you in camp.

509
00:41:03.595 --> 00:41:05.929
Maybe this is the moment

510
00:41:05.931 --> 00:41:10.166
When the zebra turns tables
on the lion.

511
00:41:10.168 --> 00:41:12.202
What say you. mr. Bohannon?

512
00:41:16.340 --> 00:41:18.174
- I say blood will be spilled.

513
00:41:18.176 --> 00:41:20.977
